	"fetchquestfaunling1-title": "Rohrkolbenwurzel Brühe",
	"fetchquestfaunling1-desc": "Oh, hallo! Wo ist bloß... Ach, egal. Ich hätte da eine Bitte, falls du kurz Zeit für mich hast... Ich koche gerade eine herrliche Suppe und brauche noch Rohrkolbenwurzeln für die Brühe. Könntest du mir welche besorgen? Ich gebe dir dafür auch ein paar Beeren!",
	"fetchquestfaunling1-obj": "Rohrkolbenwurzel {0}/4",
	"fetchquestfaunling2-title": "Verwundet",
	"fetchquestfaunling2-desc": "Ah... es sticht immer noch...\nOh, hallo... Willst du den Job zu Ende bringen? Nicht..?\nDann hilf mir bitte: Ich brauche Schachtelhalm für meine Wunden. Was an Umschlägen übrig bleibt, gebe ich dir gerne ab.",
	"fetchquestfaunling2-obj": "Schachtelhalm {0}/15",
	"fetchquestfaunling3-title": "Nur in Fall",
	"fetchquestfaunling3-desc": "Hallo, werter Abenteurer! Ich rüste mich gerade für eine lange Reise zu fernen Freunden, aber ich brauche unbedingt noch Schachtelhalm! Ein nützliches Kraut, man weiß nie, wann man mal in der Klemme steckt. Ich habe hier diese alte Tasche, die ich dir im Tausch geben würde... Würdest du mir helfen?",
	"fetchquestfaunling3-obj": "Schachtelhalm {0}/10",
	"fetchquestfaunling4-title": "Flint Arrowheads For Bed",
	"fetchquestfaunling4-desc": "How dreadful..! I'm no good at shaping stones, but I need arrowheads to fight the rot walkers.. And wolves..\nIf you make me some flint arrowheads, I'll give you.. My bedroll! I can make another of those.. Deal?",
	"fetchquestfaunling4-obj": "Flint Arrowheads {0}/18",
	"fetchquestfaunling5-title": "New Pottery",
	"fetchquestfaunling5-desc": "Hello!\nI have some bro.. Worn pots that need replacing. If you get me some clay to make new pots, I will give you the old ones.",
	"fetchquestfaunling5-obj": "Clay {0}/20",
	"fetchquestfaunling6-title": "Peat For Good Soil",
	"fetchquestfaunling6-desc": "Why do I have to mix the dirt.. Oh, hi!\nI was just mixing some dirt, but it doesn't burn like the root-dirt.. I think you call it peat?\nAnyways, if you get me some peat, I'll give you this dirt I mixed! It grows plants very well at least..",
	"fetchquestfaunling6-obj": "Peat Brick {0}/24",
	"fetchquestfaunling7-title": "Vegetables For Foraged Goods",
	"fetchquestfaunling7-desc": "All this stuff, but no vegetables.. Hey, you!\nI've been searching for vegetables, but found all this other stuff..\nI'll trade you what I've found for 20 vegetables! Come on, it's good stuff!",
	"fetchquestfaunling7-obj": "Vegetables {0}/20",
	"fetchquestfaunling8-title": "Vegetables For Mushrooms",
	"fetchquestfaunling8-desc": "Oh.. I hope this will do.. Hey, hello!\nI was asked to find vegetables, but I found all these mushrooms instead! Much better, in my opinion..\nHey, I'll trade you my mushrooms if you have any vegetables! So, do you have any?",
	"fetchquestfaunling8-obj": "Vegetable {0}/12",
	"fetchquestfaunling9-title": "Need Stink Gone",
	"fetchquestfaunling9-desc": "Phew! I tried to store my milk, but it got hard and smells funny..\nMaybe you will like what's left, traveller? You can have it, if you get me some tree fruits!",
	"fetchquestfaunling9-obj": "Tree Fruit {0}/12",
	"fetchquestfaunling10-title": "Shells For Shiny Junk",
	"fetchquestfaunling10-desc": "Why would someone want this..? Oh hi traveller!\nI have a trade for you.. I want a shell, and I'll give you this shiny thing.",
	"fetchquestfaunling10-obj": "Shells {0}/1",
	"fetchquestfaunling11-title": "Shells For Fancy Stone",
	"fetchquestfaunling11-desc": "Hello!\nI found these fancy stones from a broken old building.. I'll trade them to you for.. Some shells! Deal?",
	"fetchquestfaunling11-obj": "Shells {0}/2",
	"fetchquestfaunling12-title": "Broken Reed Chest",
	"fetchquestfaunling12-desc": "Oh, not again..!\nTraveller, my reed chest broke.. Find or make me a new one and I'll share shiny tool I found.",
	"fetchquestfaunling12-obj": "Reed Chest {0}/1",
	"fetchquestfaunling13-title": "Too Lazy To Hunt",
	"fetchquestfaunling13-desc": "Say, wanderer.. I need a big hide for sleeping in. I found some shiny arrowheads, and will trade them to you so I can take a nap.",
	"fetchquestfaunling13-obj": "Hide Large/Huge {0}/1",
	"fetchquestfaunling14-title": "Vines For Vessels",
	"fetchquestfaunling14-desc": "Hey!\nI need more rope for fishing.. I can give you this cracked pot if you get me some. I found it like this, I promise!",
	"fetchquestfaunling14-obj": "Vines {0}/12",
	"fetchquestfaunling15-title": "Misuse Of Bees",
	"fetchquestfaunling15-desc": "Come here, traveller!\nA friend played a mean trick on me, so I want bees to put in his bed.. I travel far, and have these bamboo seeds to trade.",
	"fetchquestfaunling15-obj": "Beenade Filled {0}/1",
	"killquestfaunling1-title": "Nasty Wolves",
	"killquestfaunling1-desc": "Oh, wanderer..\nI am having trouble with feral wolves.. If you could cull them in size, I'll give you this needle and thread to fix your clothes!",
	"killquestfaunling1-obj": "Wolves Killed {0}/2",
	"killquestfaunling2-title": "Honey Thief",
	"killquestfaunling2-desc": "Maybe you can help me, adventurer!\n A bear keeps stealing our honey and breaking our beehives..\nI'll give you this lost little horse, if you get rid of the bear. Maybe the bear got this youngling's parents, too..",
	"killquestfaunling2-obj": "Bear Killed {0}/1",
	"killquestfaunling3-title": "Dire Wolf",
	"killquestfaunling3-desc": "Please help, wanderer..\nA really big wolf chased me away from home..! I think I lost it, but if you find and get rid of it, I'll give you two chickens for your trouble! Please, help me!",
	"killquestfaunling3-obj": "Dire Wolf Killed {0}/1",
	"killquestfaunling4-title": "Salty Vengence",
	"killquestfaunling4-desc": "Help me get revenge!\nMy kin was dragged into the deeps by a shadow of teeth and fins! Slay this creature to put them at rest and I'll give you the salt of our tears..",
	"killquestfaunling4-obj": "Shark Killed {0}/1",
	"gamblequestfaunling1-title": "Nature's Tricksters",
	"gamblequestfaunling1-desc": "Say traveller, would you like to play a little game with me? No tricks I promise...",
	"gamblequestfaunling1-obj": "Hehehehe",
